<div style="max-width: 560px; padding: 20px; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 5px; margin: 40px auto; font-family: Open Sans,Helvetica,Arial; font-size: 15px; color: #666;">
<div style="color: #444444; font-weight: normal;">
<div style="text-align: center; font-weight: 600; font-size: 26px; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: solid 3px #eeeeee;">Hello!</div>
<div style="clear: both;"> </div>
</div>
<div style="padding: 0 30px 30px 30px; border-bottom: 3px solid #eeeeee;">
<p style="padding-top: 30px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 30px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left;">We received your request for your password to be reset.</p>
<p style="padding-top: 30px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 30px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left;">Please click on the link below and update your password to a new password of your choice. This link is valid only for 24 hours. </p>
<div style="padding: 10px 0 50px 0; text-align: center;"><a style="background: #555555; color: #fff; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 3px; letter-spacing: 0.3px;" href="{password_reset_link}">Reset your password</a></div>
<div style="padding: 15px; background: #eee; border-radius: 3px; text-align: center;">If you did not request a password reset, please ignore the link and send us an email at <a href="mailto:support@showcaseindia.com">support@showcaseindia.com</a>. </div>
</div>
<div style="color: #999; padding: 20px 30px;">
<div>Thank you,</div>
<div>Team <a style="color: #3ba1da; text-decoration: none;" href="{site_url}">{site_name}</a> </div>
</div>
</div>